Some general points:

- Text width should be around 72 characters long. (This is
  so it's easy to see changes when diffing between versions.
- If you're not sure, use US English.
- For really short links, use `[text](url)`, but for links 
  longer than ? characters, use `[text][alias]` and then define
  `[alias]: url` somewhere else in the document (usually right
  after the first occurrence of the link.